<h3><strong>外國學生入學應繳交資料(Additional Documents Required by Department)</strong></h3><ol><li>自傳(Autobiography)</li><li>讀書計畫(Study Plan)</li><li>推薦信兩封(Two Letters of Recommendation)</li><li>中文能力證明(Evidence of Chinese Proficiency)<ol><li>在中學以上學校或教育相關機構取得華語修課成績單或修課證明書</li><li>通過國家華語測驗推動工作委員會(SC-TOP)的基礎及測驗&nbsp;<br>Chinese language training certificate from accredit school/institute OR Pass TOCFL (Test of Chinese as a Foreign Language) for Basic level</li></ol></li></ol>